      "keyPoints": [
        "For emphasis: ضَرَبْتُهُ ضَرْبًا",
        "For number: ضَرَبْتُهُ ضَرْبَتَيْنِ",
        "For type: ضَرَبْتُهُ ضَرْبًا شَدِيدًا",
        "Can be replaced by synonyms or related words"
      ],
      "examples": [
